content: The cultural center owned by the central Ilbo located at the intersection of Seosomun Unfortunately, a large-scale construction is underway. Currently, a crosswalk is under construction at the entrance, so it seems difficult to have a room for a while.
There are many things to eat and see around, so it's good. I want to come again next time. I definitely want to come back next time.
Pyeongchon Park is the central park! There are many parks in this neighborhood.
